- Actor::Proxy should be able to stop the actor
- Actors created in spec examples should be stopped when the example is completed
- Messages should be able to be given a priority
- Actors should be monitored and perhaps restarted if they die
- A mixin should be provided to encrypt all messages through a mailbox via extend, or including it in inheriting Mailbox classes
- A worker pool api should be provided for mailboxes that are capable of it, e.g.,. Redis